tags.description: Start line of Oak Hill parkrun, only marked during event

tags.note: Although signed as part of a cycle route, this path and bridge over the railway is the station footbridge and cycles must be pushed.
This is the station footbridge for Oakleigh Park station and is not a cycle path, simply a footpath along which bikes can be pushed.

tags.description: Blue sign instructs cyclists to dismount and use the zebra crossing to continue on the cycle route.
